NETS at LAKERS | NBA PRESEASON FULL GAME HIGHLIGHTS | October 3, 2021

The Brooklyn Nets defeated the Los Angeles Lakers, 123-97. Cam Thomas led all scorers with 21 PTS and 4 REB for the Nets, while Paul Millsap added 10 PTS and 10 REB in the victory. Malik Monk tallied a team-high 15 PTS for the Lakers, while Anthony Davis added 6 PTS in 11 minutes of play in the losing effort. The Nets improve to 1-0 in the preseason, while the Lakers fall to 0-1.

Next Games:
Milwaukee Bucks vs. Brooklyn Nets - October 8 at 7:30pm/et on NBA TV
Los Angeles Lakers vs. Phoenix Suns - October 6 at 6pm/et on NBA TV
